data.name: ReadCsePersonAddress1

data.name: ReadEmploymentEmployerDomesticEmployerAddress
data.value: select T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.TYPE, T1.LAST_QTR_INCOME, T1.LAST_QTR, T1.LAST_QTR_YR, T1.SECOND_QTR_INCOME, T1.SECOND_QTR, T1.SECOND_QTR_YR, T1.THIRD_QTR_INCOME, T1.THIRD_QTR, T1.THIRD_QTR_YR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_INCOME, T1.FOURTH_QTR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_YR, T1.RETURN_DT, T1.RETURN_CD, T1.NAME, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CSP_I_NUMBER, T1.EMP_ID, T1.START_DT, T1.END_DT, T2.EIN, T2.NAME, T2.PHONE_NO, T2.AREA_CODE, T3.LOCATION_TYPE, T3.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T3.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T3.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T3.CREATED_BY, T3.STREET1, T3.STREET2, T3.CITY, T3.IDENTIFIER, T3.[STATE], T3.ZIP_CODE, T3.ZIP4, T3.ZIP3, T3.COUNTY from CKT_EMPLOYER T2 join CKT_INCOME_SOURCE T1 on (@cspINumber = T1.CSP_I_NUMBER) and (T1.TYPE in ('E', 'M')) and (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.EMP_ID) and (T1.END_DT = @endDt) join CKT_EMPLOYER_ADDR T3 on T2.IDENTIFIER = T3.EMP_ID order by T1.RETURN_DT desc

data.name: ReadHealthInsuranceCompany

data.name: ReadHealthInsuranceCoverage
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, POLICY_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, HIC_IDENTIFIER from CKT_HINS_COVERAGE where @cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER

data.name: ReadInterstateCaseInterstateApIdentification
data.value: select top(1) CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM, CCA_TRANSACTION_DT, ALT_SSN2, ALT_SSN1, OTHER_ID_INFO, EYE_COLOR, HAIR_COLOR, WEIGHT, HEIGHT_IN, HEIGHT_FT, BIRTH_PLACE_CITY, SSN, RACE, SEX, BIRTH_DATE, SUFFIX, NAME_FIRST, NAME_LAST, MIDDLE_NAME from CKT_INTERST_AP_ID where (CCA_TRANS_SER_NUM = @ccaTransSerNum) and (CCA_TRANSACTION_DT = @ccaTransactionDt)
